name: Individual 200k Countdown
description:
Individual 200k Countdown with a seed based on the viewer's tezos-address, renders differently for every viewer. This OBJKT displays a countdown to 200'000 minted OBJKTs! Will transform into something new, when the countdown has ended. Only refreshes on page-refresh.

Uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. - @TeNinEightNFTs
